author: Colin Bowles
title: Logano Sweeps Contender Round
text:
Logano Sweeps Contender Round - WVVA TV Bluefield Beckley WV News, Weather and Sports Member Center: 
The CampingWorld.com 500 at Talladega Superspeedway represented the final race of the Contender Round of the Chase for the NASCAR Sprint Cup, and Joey Logano officially swept the round by winning at Charlotte, Kansas and now Talladega.
